turns.utterance: Hey! I like to run Track and Field, have you ever heard of it? It is a sport that includes running, jumping and throwing.
turns.response: Oh really, im not too familiar with track but it sounds hard

turns.utterance: Track can definitely be difficult. I mostly do sprints, but there are longer distance events and races with hurdles. I am not that good yet!
turns.response: It takes time, having the guts to stick to something that exhausting is a feat in and of itself

turns.utterance: Yeah I am experiencing that dedication right now! My trainer has me working on my jumps - long jump, high jump, and triple jump.
turns.response: Man that sounds so difficult and tiring, i couldnt stick to it at all if i tried

turns.utterance: Yeah. I am already pretty good at shot put though. Have you heard of it? It is one of the throwing events of Track and Sport.
turns.response: Im not sure actually, what is that?

turns.utterance: You basically throw a heavy ball as far as you can, and the winner is the athlete who achieves the greatest distance.
turns.response: oh thats part of track and field? I didnt know that.
